## ⭐ Skill Rating System
Players rate their skills using a smooth star slider (1–10) during profile setup.
- Slider goes from 1 to 10 with smooth animation
- Each skill: dribbling, shooting, passing, speed, heading, stamina
- Strengths → skills rated 7–10 (computed automatically)
- Weaknesses → skills rated 1–4 (computed automatically)
- Never use a text input for skill ratings — always the star slider widget
- The slider must feel smooth and satisfying to use

