## 🤖 AI Coach Feature
Every player profile has a personal AI coach section with tabs:

### 🥗 Meal Plan Tab
- Calls POST /meal-plan on Python AI service
- Input: age (from dateOfBirth), height, weight, position
- Output: daily calories, protein, carbs, fats + match/training/rest day meals
- Football players ONLY — NOT bodybuilders, NOT runners
- Position-specific and age-specific calculations

### 🎯 Drill Recommender Tab
- Calls POST /recommend-drills on Python AI service
- Input: all skill ratings (1–10)
- Output: specific drills targeting weak skills with explanations
- Each recommendation maps to a real drill in the DB

### 🏥 Recovery Plan Tab (when injured)
- Calls POST /recovery-plan on Python AI service
- Input: injuryType, bodyPart, severity, playerProfile
- Output: recovery nutrition + safe rehabilitation exercises
- Only visible when player has an ACTIVE InjuryRecord

